title: Kennedy.2015.07.21.WS.SDTV.x264-XAiO
description:
"Kennedy" is a news panel show hosted by Kennedy Montgomery. Kennedy Montgomery is a libertarian that you may recognize from 90's MTV, Stossel, and the Independents.

_,-'2_,-'2_,-'2_,-'2_,-'2_,-'2_,-'2_,-'2_,-'2_,-'2

Kennedy goes through the Republican presidential contenders. She goes through every candidate using a tinder style swipe left or right.

The panel tonight consists of JOE DEVITO, JAMIE WEINSTEIN, and JOANNA NOSUCHINSKY. They continue to discuss the 16 Republican potentials. They give their top 3.
They move on to Hillary's new snapchat campaign ad. Afterwards, Hillary Clinton vs Mitch McConnel. Much talk about the "gender card".

Our panel returns to talk about Martin O'Malley's claim that global warming contributed to the rise of ISIS.

TAMAR JACOBY is here to talk about the "sanctuary city" fight and immigration.

We've got the panel back to talk about an angry restaurant owner yelling at a crying baby, Stephen Hawking puts up 100 million dollars looking for aliens.

GEORGE DURAN of TLC's Ultimate Cook-off is here to talk Twinkies. Twinkie pies, twinkie wedding cakes, twinkie tiramisu. He even brings some bacon wrapped deep fried
chocolate covered twinkies into studio. Where's Jimmy Failla?

Nightcap: Mailbag!
